ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 198, British Columbia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 198 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of BRITISH COLUMBIA, with respect to the HEAVY RAINFALL, that affected the province on June 15 to 17, 2016.
